[1] Cases in various countries

Americas
South America
---
Paraguay. 24 Nov 2022. (reported) 531 cases.
https://outbreaknewstoday.com/paraguay-dengue-and-chikungunya-cases-on-the-rise-11238/

Brazil
- National. 28 Dec 2022. (reported) 172 082 probable cases; deaths 93, more than 40% in Ceara state. Regions with highest incidence per 100 000 population: Northeast (257.1 cases), Midwest (36.1 cases), North (26.4 cases); municipality most affected: Forteleza 760 cases per 100 000 inhabitants -- nearly 10 times the national average.
https://outbreaknewstoday.com/brazil-chikungunya-shows-increase-in-cases-compared-to-2019-2019/

- Rio Grande do Norte state. 30 Nov 2022. (reported) as of 22 Oct 2022 4205 cases, compared with 1679 cases last year [2021].
https://g1.globo.com/rn/rio-grande-do-norte/noticia/2022/11/30/rn-tem-aumento-de-mais-de-800percent-nos-casos-confirmados-de-dengue-em-2022.ghtml [in Portuguese]

- Tocatins state. 8 Dec 2022. (reported) 4046 cases, more than the 292 cases in 2021 and a more than 1000% increase.
https://g1.globo.com/to/tocantins/noticia/2022/12/08/diagnosticos-de-chikungunya-crescem-mais-de-1000percent-no-to-e-estado-fica-em-situacao-de-alerta-explosao-de-casos.ghtml [in Potuguese]

Asia
---
Philippines. 27 Dec 2022. (reported). 593 cases, 566% higher than during 2021. Regions most affected: Calabarzon 154 cases; Central Visayas 127 cases; Davao 111 cases.
https://www.philstar.com/headlines/2022/12/27/2233456/doh-593-chikungunya-cases-reported-nationwide

